net.rim.device.api.collection
Interface IntKeyProviderAdaptor

public interface IntKeyProviderAdaptor

Adaptor class that can retrieve integer keys for collections that can use them.

IntSortedReadableList collections can make use of objects implementing this interface to extract the integer keys it requires from its contained elements.

Whether this key is actually contained in the element object, or whether it is generated by the adaptor itself based on other data contained in the element, is up to the implementor.
